OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FCloudy with spells of rain and
OL,6,Fstrong winds at first. This generally
OL,7,Fclearing by late morning, though
OL,8,Fshowers are expected to develop in the
OL,9,Fafternoon, perhaps turning heavy at
OL,10,Ftimes.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,13,FUnsettled over the weekend with strong
OL,14,Fwinds and outbreaks of rain and
OL,15,Fshowers, turning heavy at times. Dry
OL,16,Fon Monday with lighter winds and some
OL,17,Fsunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
